The paper discusses a soft attention model for reinforcement learning, which involves machine learning, artificial intelligence, computer vision, natural language processing, and robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.RO (Robotics).
